<p><strong>How to Research an Answer </strong></p>
<p><span>{{How to conduct research through Project pages short version|content; float:right}}</span>Follow these steps or watch this video demonstrating how to research and add answers:</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>Select the company, metric and year</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Look for the answer to the metric's question in a suggested source or add a new source</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Cite the source</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the answer and supporting comments</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Submit!</p>
</li>
</ol>